snippet.title: Amber Heard Responds To Losing ALL Movie Roles
snippet.description:
Amber Heard Responds To Losing ALL Movie Roles


In the Hollywood world, everyone wants to get that big role that will forever put you in the spotlight, usually getting one of those means that you will keep getting the same type of roles and stay as an A-list actor or actress proving time and time again how you can cover a variety of important roles. For Amber Heard this moment happened when she got her dream role as Mera in Aquaman but it seems she won’t be able to carry on the momentum and get more jobs in the business.
